Subject: [PATCH 4/5] preemption: add ETHTOOL_A_PREEMPT_STATUS netlink
 atrribute

From https://github.com/nxp-real-time-edge-sw/meta-real-time-edge/blob/mickledore/recipes-extended/ethtool/files/0004-preemption-add-ETHTOOL_A_PREEMPT_STATUS-netlink-atrr.patch

